description: Welcome to THE ICON, a collection of 3 luxurious, waterfront homes built from the ground up by prominent developers with extreme attention to detail. This sprawling 2,500 sf floor-through residence features ocean views, 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, private deck, private roof deck deck, 2 garage parking spaces and private elevator access. The exclusive roof deck features 360 views sprawling over 700 square feet. Artfully designed kitchens begin with oak & light gray cabinetry by Divine Design complemented by Quartz counters & backsplashes and designer Miele and Fisher Paykel appliances. The open concept living area flows onto a front facing deck with collapsible doors, allowing you to effortlessly tuck them away and bring the living room outside. The primary suite showcases a pristine, spa-like bath with dual sinks, an oversized shower with a separate soaking tub & radiant floors. Modern luxury meets seaside living at THE ICON, a new standard for South Boston!
